data.title: Walled Lake Consolidated Schools
data.text:
The Knights have a new man at the helm, Mark Brimmer, who makes his return to Commerce Township after serving as the program’s junior varsity coach in 2022.

Read More about Walled Lake Northern hungry to right the ship under new head coach

Jeff Penrod has been a mainstay in the Walled Lake Central football program for nearly two decades, but this season he can add a new role to his resume as this is his first as the Vikings’ head coach.

Read More about Walled Lake Central football enters 2024 with a new, but familiar, face at the helm

There is no question Walled Lake Western enters 2024 with a target on its back. The Warriors have taken home the Lake Valley Conference title each of the past two seasons and are riding a 19-game conference win streak dating back to October 8, 2021.

Read More about Walled Lake Western football reloads in 2024 with its sights set on a Lakes Valley Conference 3-peat and a trip to Ford Field
